&lt;p&gt;The Cancer Services team in Wrexham Maelor Hospital is looking to recruit an enthusiastic, motivated individual to join our team of cancer multi-disciplinary team co-ordinators as team leader. We are looking for someone who can work closely with both our MDT co-ordinators and also a dedicated team of clinicians to fast track patients through the cancer pathway, provide administrative support to the weekly clinical team meeting, where all new patients are discussed and optimum treatment plans agreed, and collate clinical data on the dedicated national cancer database whilst also providing support to the management team. In addition to this they will provide support and leadership&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing date: 11/11/20&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
